              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "Paper introduces a new approach using multi-criteria integer programming for team formation. The model considers multiple factors including skill level, background and personality traits. Algorithm focuses on maximizing whithin-group differences while minizing between-group differences. ",
                "link": null
              },
